data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Own this beautiful cottage style home! Home backs up to field pasture. Rear deck and paver patio off of master bedroom. Fully updated house with a walk in closet, shop also has a loft, and a cute shed in the backyard. Home has lots of storage, closets, new ductless heating and a/c installed last year. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms and living room. Next to schools, hospitals, YMCA, parks, etc. Come take a look!
